				Some good points from Brad, I played a lot of MUD at University and then went onto play Quake &amp; Unreal etc.  So it was natural progression to move to a first person MUD =P<BR>
<BR>
To Brad and the gang,<BR>
<BR>
This has to be the best game I have played.  The balance between experiencing new areas and making friends is very balanced, being in a guild can be detrimental (All that green spam makes you miss important messages ;P), although the benefits far out weigh not being in a guild.<BR>
<BR>
I have only 1 problem with the game, Farmers.<BR>
<BR>
Please sort either the Auction site problem, by enforcing new rules to stop these people who are really hurting the EQ Economy with $=Plat<BR>
